ISLAMABAD, Sep 7 (APP): Minister for Foreign Affairs Shah Mahmood Qureshi Tuesday called on Prime Minister Imran Khan and discussed Afghanistan as well as the regional situation.
Qureshi, who is also the vice chairman of Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf, also discussed with prime minister the party matters and overall political situation of the country.
